graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    TrustyAI -->|required| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.19+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    TrustyAI -->|inference monitoring| KServe[KServe 0.12.1+]
    TrustyAI -->|traffic routing<br/>VirtualService<br/>DestinationRule| Istio[Istio Latest]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics collection<br/>ServiceMonitor| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator 0.64.1]
    TrustyAI -->|job queueing<br/>LMEvalJob| Kueue[Kueue 0.6.2+]
    TrustyAI -->|routes<br/>certificates| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.6+]

    %% Storage Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|inference data| Database[(Database<br/>PostgreSQL/MySQL)]
    TrustyAI -->|filesystem storage| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim]

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -->|model/dataset download| HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|API calls<br/>patching| KServeInference[KServe InferenceService]
    TrustyAI -->|label selector<br/>modelmesh-service| ModelMesh[Model Mesh]

    %% Service Mesh
    TrustyAI -.->|mTLS enforcement| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio]

    %% Managed Components
    TrustyAI -->|deploys| TrustyAIService[TrustyAI Service<br/>Deployment]
    TrustyAI -->|deploys| GuardrailsOrch[Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>Deployment]
    TrustyAI -->|deploys| NemoGuard[Nemo Guardrails<br/>Deployment]
    TrustyAI -->|creates| LMEvalJob[LM Evaluation Job<br/>Job/Pod]

    %% Component interactions
    TrustyAIService -->|monitors| KServeInference
    GuardrailsOrch -->|routes through| KServeInference
    LMEvalJob -->|evaluates| KServeInference

